No pude prevenir a tu marido.

534
00:27:45,650 --> 00:27:46,790
Tendrás que hacerlo tú.

535
00:27:46,910 --> 00:27:48,750
Y antes de que lo interroguen, ¿eh?

536
00:27:48,770 --> 00:27:49,770
¿Y si nos separan? Pues.

537
00:27:50,430 --> 00:27:50,830
..

538
00:27:50,831 --> 00:27:51,991
Tal vez te lo puedo decir yo.

539
00:27:52,250 --> 00:27:53,590
Antes de que nos despidamos.

540
00:27:53,810 --> 00:27:54,810
Ay, sí.

541
00:27:54,950 --> 00:27:55,350
Claro.

542
00:27:55,470 --> 00:27:55,810
¿Qué?

543
00:27:55,970 --> 00:27:56,970
Sí.

544
00:27:57,950 --> 00:27:58,950
Matilde.

545
00:27:59,310 --> 00:27:59,710
Escúchame.

546
00:28:00,290 --> 00:28:01,330
Saca la casta.

547
00:28:02,830 --> 00:28:04,270
Muéstrate tranquila y segura.

548
00:28:04,450 --> 00:28:04,850
